// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-2334 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 0352dcbb-28df-5317-9d28-f543636f636a

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:7*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:8*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:16.04-ESM*")
